==個人生活==
達克生涯一共有兩段婚姻，第一段婚姻以離婚收場，後來又結了第二次婚。他與第一任妻子育有4個小孩，並和第二位收養了2個小孩。
==晚年==
1981年，達克入選路易斯安那州立大學運動員名人堂。<ref name="LSU">{{cite web|title=LSU Athletics Hall of Fame Members|url=http://www.lsusports.net/ViewArticle.dbml?ATCLID=177326|website=LSUsports.net|access-date=2020-08-16|archive-date=2019-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902091331/http://www.lsusports.net/ViewArticle.dbml?ATCLID=177326|dead-url=yes}}</ref>5年後，他入選路易斯安那州立大學運動名人堂。<ref name=LSHOF>{{cite web|title=Alvin Ralph Dark|url=http://www.lasportshall.com/inductees/baseball/alvin-dark/|publisher=[[Louisiana_Sports_Hall_of_Fame|Louisiana Sports Hall of Fame]]|accessdate=June 19, 2016|archive-date=2016-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011062906/http://www.lasportshall.com/inductees/baseball/alvin-dark/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年11月13日，達克因為阿茲海默症在家中辭世，享耆壽92歲。<ref name="Dark"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/giants-great-alvin-dark-dead-92-article-1.2010212|title=Alvin Dark, Giants captain, shortstop and manager whose career was dogged by racial comments, dead at age 92|publisher=[[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]]|work=nydailynews.com|accessdate=November 13, 2014|date=November 13, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305075010/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/giants-great-alvin-dark-dead-92-article-1.2010212|dead-url=no}}</ref>
